						<summary>

						<p>Slab setup near a channel close to the temple of Kāṭamayya, 3 miles from the village.</p>						

						<p>It records the gift of two <hi rend="italic">maṛutus</hi> of land by Chendubāvi Amma to the god Alāḷanātha for conducting worship.</p>						

